📋 Admin Dashboard Module - Complete Documentation
Module Overview
Admin Dashboard SnapGO کا central control panel ہے جہاں سے administrators پورے system کو manage کرتے ہیں۔ یہ module real-time statistics, quick actions, اور system monitoring features فراہم کرتا ہے۔
Features & Functionality
1. Dashboard Statistics
•	Total Users: Active, inactive, اور deleted users کی تعداد
•	Active Subscriptions: Currently active subscriptions by category
•	Revenue Overview: Daily, weekly, monthly revenue tracking
•	OTP Usage: Daily OTP requests اور success rate
•	System Health: Server status, database connections, email service status
2. Quick Actions Panel
•	Add new user
•	Create new category
•	View pending payments
•	Check OTP logs
•	System announcements
3. Recent Activities
•	Latest user registrations
•	Recent subscription purchases
•	OTP request logs
•	Payment transactions
•	System alerts
4. Charts & Analytics
•	User growth chart (30 days)
•	Revenue trend graph
•	Category-wise subscription distribution
•	Peak usage hours heatmap
User Interface Design
Layout Structure
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    Header Navigation                     │
├─────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────┤
│             │                                           │
│   Sidebar   │          Main Dashboard Content          │
│             │                                           │
│  - Dashboard│  ┌─────────┐ ┌─────────┐ ┌─────────┐   │
│  - Users    │  │ Stats 1 │ │ Stats 2 │ │ Stats 3 │   │
│  - Category │  └─────────┘ └─────────┘ └─────────┘   │
│  - OTP      │                                           │
│  - Reports  │  ┌───────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  - Cleanup  │  │         Revenue Chart              │   │
│  - Settings │  └───────────────────────────────────┘   │
│             │                                           │
│             │  ┌───────────────────────────────────┐   │
│             │  │      Recent Activities             │   │
│             │  └───────────────────────────────────┘   │
└─────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────┘
Color Scheme
•	Primary: #F57224 (Orange - from original documentation)
•	Secondary: #0F146D (Dark Blue)
•	Success: #10B981
•	Warning: #F59E0B
•	Background: #F2F3F7
Responsive Design
•	Desktop: Full sidebar + content
•	Tablet: Collapsible sidebar
•	Mobile: Bottom navigation + stacked cards
Database Tables Used
1. users
sql
- user_id
- email
- full_name
- account_status
- last_login
- created_at
2. user_subscriptions
sql
- subscription_id
- user_id
- category_id
- status
- start_date
- end_date
3. payment_transactions
sql
- transaction_id
- user_id
- amount
- payment_method
- status
4. activity_logs
sql
- log_id
- user_id
- activity_type
- activity_description
- created_at
File Structure
modules/admin/
├── admin_dashboard.php       # Main dashboard file
├── admin_navigation_bar.php  # Top navigation
├── admin_sidebar.php        # Side navigation
└── dashboard_api.php        # AJAX endpoints
Key Functions
Statistics Calculation
•	getTotalUsers() - Total users count with status breakdown
•	getActiveSubscriptions() - Current active subscriptions
•	getRevenueStats($period) - Revenue for specified period
•	getOTPUsageStats() - OTP usage statistics
Chart Data Generation
•	getUserGrowthData() - 30-day user registration data
•	getRevenueChartData() - Revenue trend data
•	getCategoryDistribution() - Subscription distribution by category
AJAX Endpoints
/api/admin/dashboard/
├── get-stats.php         # Real-time statistics
├── get-activities.php    # Recent activities
├── get-chart-data.php    # Chart data
└── refresh-widget.php    # Widget refresh
Security Features
1.	Role Check: Only admin role can access
2.	Session Validation: Check admin session on each request
3.	CSRF Protection: Token validation for all actions
4.	Activity Logging: All dashboard access logged
5.	IP Restriction: Optional IP whitelist for admin access
Performance Optimization
1.	Caching: Statistics cached for 5 minutes
2.	Lazy Loading: Charts load after page render
3.	Database Indexing: Optimized queries with proper indexes
4.	Pagination: Recent activities limited to 20 items
Business Logic
Dashboard Refresh Rules
•	Statistics: Auto-refresh every 5 minutes
•	Activities: Real-time updates via WebSocket (optional)
•	Charts: Manual refresh button available
Alert Thresholds
•	Low balance alert: When wallet < 1000 THB
•	High OTP usage: > 80% of daily limit
•	Failed payments: > 5 in last hour
•	Server load: > 80% CPU usage
Mobile Responsiveness
•	320px-767px: Single column, bottom navigation
•	768px-1023px: Collapsible sidebar, 2-column grid
•	1024px+: Full sidebar, 3-column grid
Integration Points
1.	Payment APIs: Show real-time payment status
2.	Email Service: Monitor email delivery status
3.	SMS Gateway: Track SMS OTP usage
4.	System Monitoring: Server resource usage
Error Handling
•	Database connection failures: Show cached data
•	API timeouts: Display last known values
•	Invalid data: Graceful degradation
•	Permission errors: Redirect to login
Future Enhancements
1.	Real-time notifications
2.	Customizable dashboard widgets
3.	Export reports functionality
4.	Multi-language support
5.	Dark mode theme
